reviewText: The "Berry Brick Road" DVD is a very cute and interesting version of the Wizard of Oz.  It is not scary, thank goodness.

I myself love the older strawberry shortcake my 10 month old daughter has fallen in love as well this is almost like the wizard of oz. Strawberry shortcaks sets amazing examples fpr young children i plan to buy all the older versions.
My daughter loves strawberry shortcake and the wizard of oz and this movie is an adorable re telling of the wizard of oz with all the cuteness of strawberry and her friends.
Always loved these as a kid and can't believe they are still around.  Great movie and my girls love them.  Good shape.

Received the DVD very quickly, ordered for my granddaughter for Easter and she absolutely loved it, one of her favorites, that I now have watched at least 10 times.  Thanks for the great product and service.  Loretta Dinges

Perfect!  Grand Child's Birthday Gift.  They will continue to view and view this video for years to come.  In short, it is a modern day redo of the classic Wizard of Oz.  Well done with all the psychology research expected to convey common sense, courtesy, respect and how to be polite, while not being taken for a ride in today's society.  Well done.  Will be giving this series to grand kids instead of gifts in the future.  Pleasantly surprised....
Shipped out very quickly and arrived sooner than expected. The only surprise was that a hook on the inside was cracked off. Other than that my sister loved it and I am happy with my purchase.
My granddaughter loves this movie. Her first love was Wizard of Oz and when she watched this for the first time it was an instant favorite.
Very sweet version of the classic. Perfect for little ones who may be frightened of some of the stranger details of the original. My 2 and 3 year olds absolutely love it!
